{"id": "art-129", "label": "Art. 129", "title": "Art. 129", "slug": "art-129", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 129 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2068594364\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2288\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2068594364\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În ziua <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> la ora\nar&#259;tate în convocare, <span class=SpellE>&#351;edin&#355;a</span>\nadun&#259;rii se va deschide de c&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edintele</span>\nconsiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv al\ndirectoratului, sau de c&#259;tre acela care îi <span class=SpellE>&#355;ine</span>\nlocul.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1847382873\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2287\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1847382873\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Adunarea general&#259; va alege, dintre <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> <span class=SpellE>prezen&#355;i</span>, 1\npân&#259; la 3 secretari, care vor verifica lista de <span class=SpellE>prezen&#355;&#259;</span>\na <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, indicând capitalul social pe\ncare îl reprezint&#259; fiecare, procesul-verbal întocmit de secretarul tehnic\npentru constatarea num&#259;rului <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>\ndepuse <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> îndeplinirea tuturor <span\nclass=SpellE>formalit&#259;&#355;ilor</span> cerute de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>lege</i> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de actul constitutiv pentru <span\nclass=SpellE>&#355;inerea</span> adun&#259;rii generale.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Adunarea general&#259; va putea\nhot&#259;rî ca <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunile</span> prev&#259;zute în\nalineatul precedent s&#259; fie supravegheate sau îndeplinite de un notar\npublic, pe cheltuiala <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)Unul dintre secretari <span\nclass=SpellE>întocme&#351;te</span> procesul-verbal al <span class=SpellE>&#351;edin&#355;ei</span>\nadun&#259;rii generale.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1246536380\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2286\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1246536380\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)<span class=SpellE>Pre&#351;edintele</span> va putea\ndesemna, dintre <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\nunul sau mai <span class=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span> secretari tehnici, care\ns&#259; ia parte la executarea <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute la alineatele precedente.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(6)Dup&#259; constatarea\nîndeplinirii <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;elor</span> legale <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a prevederilor actului constitutiv pentru <span\nclass=SpellE>&#355;inerea</span> adun&#259;rii generale, se intr&#259; în\nordinea de zi.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1742411617\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2285\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1742411617\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Nu pot fi adoptate hot&#259;râri asupra unor puncte de\npe ordinea de zi care nu au fost publicate în conformitate cu <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span> art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>117</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 117<sup>1</sup>, cu <span\nclass=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> cazului în care <span class=SpellE>to&#355;i</span>\n<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> au fost <span class=SpellE>prezen&#355;i</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>reprezenta&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nniciunul dintre <span class=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span> nu s-a opus sau nu a\ncontestat aceast&#259; hot&#259;râre.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}